DataSet.Description: Data listing the position an individual holds at a university and their academic history

DataSet.Description: School BS was received and school PhD was received
DataSet.EdgeType: Faculty member received the BS from u and received their PhD from v
DataSet.GraphProperties: Weighted integer, Multigraph, Temporal snapshots, Directed

DataSet.Name: top205_PhD-AllFaculty_matrix
DataSet.Description: University Working at and University PhD was recived from. This graph inclues all tenure track staff members
DataSet.EdgeType: Number of faculty currently working at university j and recived their PhD at university i
DataSet.GraphProperties: Weighted integer, Multigraph, Temporal snapshots, Directed

DataSet.Name: top205_PhD-Assistant_matrix
DataSet.Description: University Working at and University PhD was recived from. This graph inclues all tenure track staff members who are currently assistants
DataSet.EdgeType: Number of faculty currently working at university j and recived their PhD at university i
DataSet.GraphProperties: Weighted integer, Multigraph, Temporal snapshots, Directed

DataSet.Name: top205_PhD-Associate_matrix
DataSet.Description: University Working at and University PhD was recived from. This graph inclues all tenure track staff members who are currently associates
DataSet.EdgeType: Number of faculty currently working at university j and recived their PhD at university i
DataSet.GraphProperties: Weighted integer, Multigraph, Temporal snapshots, Directed

DataSet.Name: top205_PhD-Full_matrix
DataSet.Description: University Working at and University PhD was recived from. This graph inclues all tenure track staff members who hold a full position
DataSet.EdgeType: Number of faculty currently working at university j and recived their PhD at university i
DataSet.GraphProperties: Weighted integer, Multigraph, Temporal snapshots, Directed
